A shinning symbol of great craftsmanship and aesthetics is this exquisitely created women’s analog timepiece from the designer house of FCUK. With a host of specialized design elements this watch makes a perfect choice for the modern day woman who loves to have fun party and standout in a crowd.

The timekeeping function on this FCUK women’s watch operates using the popular quartz crystal technology. This process works by generating an electrical charge which causes the crystals to vibrate at a thousand times a second making them extremely stable resonators for accurate timekeeping.

Body and Design

This highly stylized women’s timepiece from FCUK is built around a round dial that has a diameter of 31 mm. This very compact round dial contains a watch face with a dark coloured background over which we find the three watch hands that carry a bright and shiny metallic finish. Even the hour markers which are small rectangular bars apart from the 3 6 9 and 12-hour marker which are represented by numeric markers also carry a similar metallic finish as the watch hands. This clever use of metallic elements against a dark background not only adds to the style of the dial but also gives you clear and undisturbed reading of the dial. 

This thoughtfully conceived dial is enveloped by a very aesthetic stainless steel case that is designed to offer the dial considerable protection against impacts and shocks. Keeping this attractive dial comfortably attached to you wrist is the watch’s extremely stylish strap.

The dial is capped with a highly durable and scratch-resistant mineral glass cover which along with the stainless steel case gives the dial the all-important aspect of water resistance. With such an assortment of desirable attributes to its credit this overwhelming timepiece from FCUK is sure to make you standout and shine everywhere you go.

FCUK Analog Watch - For Women (Silver) Price: Rs.8495

Key Features

  • Round Dial
  • Steel Case
  • Silver Strap
  • Water Resistant

From the stables of the world-renowned international fashion brand FCUK comes this graceful and good looking women’s analog watch that features a generous amount of chrome and crystal studs making it as much a fashion accessory as it is a reliable personal timekeeping device.

Body and Design

This highly stylized women’s timepiece from FCUK features an extremely attractive round dial that carries a significant amount of semi-precious crystals on and around it. Inside this dial is a watch face that carries a very dominant dark colour as its background. The crystal studs are arranged along the outer perimeter of the watch face with each of the crystals acting as an hour marker. There are very discreet minute markings along the outermost track of the dial which are given a light colour. The watch’s three time indicating hands are given a bright metallic finish making them easily identifiable against the dark background thus providing for hassle-free time reading.

This dial is enveloped by a well-built steel case that is designed to offer a considerable level of protection from low level impacts and shocks. This casing sports a crystal embellished bezel with a fine metallic finish. Another key design element within the dial is a crystal studded FCUK logo formation at the middle of the watch face which adds a great deal to the watch’s overall aesthetics. This very attractive and stylish dial is held in place comfortably attached to your wrist with an extremely classy stainless steel strap.

Functions and Other Features

The time on the dial can be adjusted as needed by using the rotating crown which is on the right side of the dial’s case. This well-built steel case along with a clear glass dial cover gives this graceful and elegant women’s watch a water-resistant capability of up to 30 m. In all this highly stylized personal timepiece from FCUK gives you everything from an eye-catching fashion accessory to a durable and accurate personal timekeeping device.
